title: Businessweek Extra- Carnival CEO Arnold Donald

description:
Carnival Corporation CEO Arnold Donald joins from Bloomberg’s The Year Ahead virtual event to discuss the future of the cruise line industry.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Doni Holloway.
